OL,5, Mounting delays at the Passport Office 
OL,6, have forced would-be holidaymakers to  
OL,7, queue for hours to receive their       
OL,8, documents during Monday's heatwave.    
OL,10,FOfficials have previously said that    
OL,11,Fpeople should allow 10 weeks for       
OL,12,Fapproval of a new passport.            
OL,14,FBut many of those who spoke to BBC News
OL,15,Fin London said they had been waiting   
OL,16,Fmuch longer.                           
OL,18,FThe Passport Office said 98.5% of the 3
OL,19,Fmillion recent applications were       
OL,20,Fcompleted within 10 weeks.             
